μ«μμ™€ μ κ³± κ°’ λ”•μ…”λ„λ¦¬

numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
squared_dict = {x: x**2 for x in numbers}
print(squared_dict)  # μ¶λ ¥: {1: 1, 2: 4, 3: 9, 4: 16, 5: 25}
μ΅°κ±΄μ„ ν¬ν•¨ν• λ”•μ…”λ„λ¦¬

even_squared_dict = {x: x**2 for x in numbers if x % 2 == 0}
print(even_squared_dict)  # μ¶λ ¥: {2: 4, 4: 16}
λ¬Έμμ—΄μ„ ν‚¤μ™€ κ°’μΌλ΅ λ³€ν™

word = "hello"
