print(squared_set)  # μ¶λ ¥: {1, 4, 9, 16, 25}
μ΅°κ±΄μ„ ν¬ν•¨ν• μ„ΈνΈ

even_set = {x for x in numbers if x % 2 == 0}
print(even_set)  # μ¶λ ¥: {2, 4}

4. λΉ„κµ
